reviews.review_msg: They are a great professor. Lectures were good and grades were fair. They have the best syllabus I have ever read and are willing to accommodate every student no matter what. I would take a class with this prof again, it really changed my thoughts on disability. If you show up to class and demonstrate that you care - you will do really well.

A.J. is a really kind and caring prof. They were very clear with grading criteria and expectations for assignments. They were very accessible outside of class during office hours and via email. You can tell A.J. actually cares about their students and is very understanding.
